    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The dragging works differently from the older editor, it won't place the tile unless all underlying cells are blank when dragging -- except for the initial click. Maybe that behavior could be configurable but I feel the actual problem is there's no quick way to paint water (and to a lesser extent ra interior floors) so maybe a fill area tool gets around this.\n"
