    "body": "As @cjshmyr mentioned, this is the expected behaviour.  If you drag the mouse with a 2x2 or larger template it requires all the tiles under the footprint to be of a different template to what you are placing.  If we didn't do that then you would end up with a dragged line of just one edge of the template.\n"
